{"type": "article", "id": 28569, "title": "其实我们逛杂货店的时候，也在消费杂货店的设计", "description": "增加实体店的购物趣味，这家店的做法可以参考。", "date": "2016-06-22T12:51:07Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 29293, "name": "杂货店"}, {"id": 29294, "name": "Editor Market"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 3, "praise_count": 179, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160703124219AQ7B9yOKstJd6UmW.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p>          </p>\n<p>当你在逛街时应该会发现，一些卖日常生活品的商店多了起来，产品的种类丰富且有一定的设计感，店铺布置得也挺文艺。有些店里会放上独立设计师的名牌，或者成为引进国外品牌的买手店，我们常常笼统地称它们为“杂货店”，而产品本身的设计和稀有又能成为时尚潮人聚集的地方。</p>\n<p>在阿根廷首都布宜诺斯艾利斯的这家店 <a href=\"http://www.editormarket.com.ar\">Editor Market </a>也是类似的杂货店，但它是面积更大的一种，从占地 1200 平方米的仓库改建的。因而这里能收纳的产品很丰富，主要分为家具和服饰配件两类，汇集了不少当地的独立品牌。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124210v2MnDjE1FWYdO6cw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124210scHx5u7byzhU0JKe.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>设计团队<a href=\"http://www.anarascovsky.com/arquitectura-obras/editor-market-dorrego\"> Ana Rascovsky </a>在设计时需要在这个长 70 米的地方增加更多的“惊喜”，确保人们有耐心逛到尽头。他们使用一种白色的细长金属管做结构搭建方框形的架子和隔断，并在不同地方放上绿色盆栽做搭配，有移步换景的效果。方框结构配合白色的墙面保持了视线的空旷和通透，放在其中的物品和盆栽又起到遮挡的作用，能让人保持对其他区域的好奇。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124211i20VCWb85fNQeI9Y.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\">改造前</div></figcaption></figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031242110WLbzCBqm3dJXlfT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124212ME2vPqx9ANsLwbzJ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124212ZxCed5a9fiAJ38nR.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.61111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124213noHqzbkiwXgr3C4R.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p>阶梯也是让空间显得有层次的办法，商店本身带有一个地下空间和二楼夹层，而中间更空旷的地方就用白色的板和框子搭建出错落的平台，走两步就要上一个台阶，就像一个小的展示台，也增加了购物的趣味。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124213p6eUQBiCaFXIwqzA.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031242149ydVFqiAxtL6NePC.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124214KImlHT5qJSw637gn.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74814815\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124215Cq2QodjMuer07hsG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.49925037\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\">进门处有一个 cafe 区，这是增加购物体验的环节。<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607031242160xU9rH1LNOKhIQqD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p class=\"\">地下一楼的层高不高，减少了白色框架的遮挡，有更多靠墙而放的架子。这里主要售卖衣服。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124216kH6VerpzgywUWZIT.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124217QU7qu32OHEXRhK94.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.56296296\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p>我们报道过的买手店<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/26743.html\">“RESEE（又见）”</a>的创始人王巍曾称，实体买手店最大的问题在于“过度装修”，抬高了运营成本，“装修是最应该精打细算的部分”。这家店使用的的白色细金属管其实也是降低成本的做法，它的灵活变化也方便了以后的拆装。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124218FlJvyfTkt3qx7ODc.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.58425926\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124218S4LK2BqGCsZAUeQY.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.26666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124218emZYkWfKFxVNLr13.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.26666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160703124219EP47JUQiVXfSZvOx.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.26666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"placeholder\"></figure>\n</div>\n<p>图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.archdaily.com/789506/editor-dorrego-ana-rascovsky-arqs\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">archdaily</a>、<a href=\"http://www.editormarket.com.ar/\" style=\"background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Editor Market</a><br></p>\n\n"}